Isn't yours a name brand too?

6
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,000
Mine...

7
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:07,280
Look at mine.

8
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:11,080
I just bought this.

9
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:13,039
I asked Brother Zhang.

10
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,159
This kind is pure cotton.

11
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,599
It can't be washed out.

12
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:16,560
It's fine.

13
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,680
If it doesn't come out, just wash it again later.

14
00:02:19,159 --> 00:02:19,919
Then you wash it.

15
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:21,319
Let me wash yours for you.

16
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,280
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

17
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,400
Freezing to death.

18
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:32,960
Freezing to death isn't painful.

19
00:02:33,479 --> 00:02:34,719
You go numb, right?

20
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,560
I'm really puzzled.

21
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:39,400
Why do you keep obsessing over this?

22
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:41,479
Numbness.

23
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:43,039
You think numbness means you don't feel anything?

24
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,199
Before you go numb,

25
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:45,879
first, your body temperature

26
00:02:45,879 --> 00:02:48,879
will drop straight from thirty-seven to thirty-four degrees.

27
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,039
At that point, your whole body

28
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,280
feels like it's being pricked by needles.

29
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,240
A pain that goes right to the bone.

30
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,560
After your nerves go numb,

31
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:55,879
you'll feel

32
00:02:56,719 --> 00:02:57,319
suddenly hot.

33
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,159
You start hallucinating.

34
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,840
You might even want to take your clothes off.

35
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:01,960
I don't believe it.

36
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:04,479
I'll take a cold shower in a bit.

37
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:06,120
Then hurry up, do it now.

38
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,240
I'll do it right now.

39
00:03:15,159 --> 00:03:16,439
So, are you in the shower now?

40
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,319
It's not cold at all.

41
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,120
No, it's warm.

42
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,719
Wait a moment.

43
00:03:21,719 --> 00:03:23,000
I'll make it even warmer for you.

44
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:24,719
You go ahead and shower first.

45
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:26,919
Open the door for me.

46
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,400
You really turned on the cold water for me?

47
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,560
Are you trying to freeze me to death?

48
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:39,560
Lei, Lei, Lei!

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,639
Wow, you guys really showed up right on time.

50
00:03:44,919 --> 00:03:46,120
The crayfish are sold out.

51
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,960
What should we eat then?

52
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:48,080
No more crayfish.

53
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,120
I'm almost sick of eating them anyway.

54
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,479
Let's just eat whatever we have.

55
00:03:50,759 --> 00:03:52,400
So, how about egg fried rice?

56
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,240
Sure, sure.

57
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,280
Xiaoli.

58
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,560
Use the leftover rice in the kitchen to make some egg fried rice.

59
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:58,719
And whip up a couple of side dishes too.

60
00:03:58,719 --> 00:03:59,479
Okay!

61
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,840
You two wait for me a bit.

62
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:03,639
Okay, boss.

63
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,319
Go get me two bottles of beer from the fridge.

64
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,280
Wait, Lei.

65
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,680
Can you add two more eggs for me first?

66
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:10,680
Xiaoli.

67
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:13,000
Add two more eggs, we've got a foodie here.

68
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:13,599
Okay!

69
