Lei, the two of us can't drink.

70
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:15,159
We didn't get permission.

71
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:17,040
I'll drink.

72
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,079
You really can't take a hint.

73
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,079
Coming, coming, coming!

74
00:04:23,079 --> 00:04:24,160
Move aside, pour it.

75
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,439
This young man

76
