He's quite particular

77
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,959
He even wrapped it for me with a tissue

78
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,319
Go ahead, tell me

79
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,279
That's for Master

80
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,279
How have you been lately?

81
00:04:39,439 --> 00:04:40,680
Just learning from Master

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,839
What have you learned?

83
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,639
Lately, the two of us

84
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:44,480
have been discussing

85
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:47,279
ways to die without pain in this world

86
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,240
Ways to die without pain

87
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,959
Tell me about it

88
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,480
Suicide by cutting one's own throat

89
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:54,480
You've watched too many TV dramas.

90
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,000
Suicide by throat-cutting isn't that easy.

91
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:57,720
First, you have to find the right spot.

92
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,639
Cut through the muscle.

93
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:01,639
You have to cut both your artery and vein horizontally at the same time.

94
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,480
With your reaction speed,

95
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,879
