98
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,439
but you still wouldn't be dead yet.

99
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:11,040
You'd have to watch yourself

100
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,079
get decapitated.

101
00:05:12,279 --> 00:05:13,600
Why would I cut off my own head?

102
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:14,800
Weren't you asking about suicide by throat-cutting?

103
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,040
But I can't cut off my own head!

104
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,040
I think this kid's got it.

105
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,439
He memorizes these terms so well.

106
00:05:18,439 --> 00:05:19,319
All he can do is recite them.

107
00:05:19,399 --> 00:05:21,079
What kind of case is this, all bloody and messy?

108
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,680
It's not something you can explain in a sentence or two.

109
00:05:23,319 --> 00:05:24,120
Brother Lei,

110
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,120
you have a lot of experience.

111
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,279
Share some with me.

112
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:27,839
Is there a painless way to die?

113
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:30,079
A painless way to die?

114
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:31,879
Xiaoli,

115
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:33,759
add some arsenic to the fried rice.

116
00:05:35,839 --> 00:05:36,360
No.

117
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:39,680
Don't say that. Dying from poisoning isn't painless.

118
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:42,079
Arsenic poisoning causes stomach pain and diarrhea.

119
00:05:42,079 --> 00:05:43,160
Dizziness and headaches.

120
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,040
Fried rice is here.

121
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,319
Thank you.

122
00:05:44,319 --> 00:05:46,240
Kidney failure, liver failure.

123
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:47,800
Multiple organ failure.

124
00:05:47,879 --> 00:05:48,680
What are you talking about?

125
00:05:50,279 --> 00:05:51,319
What do you mean by that?

126
00:05:51,319 --> 00:05:52,839
What, is this not enough food?

127
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:54,399
What?

128
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:55,879
Here.

129
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:56,879
Thanks, Lei.

130
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,079
Stewed pork.

131
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:04,199
Looks like we're on a case today.

132
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,959
Hurry up and eat, come on.

133
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,759
You can really eat at a time like this.

134
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,480
Eat, starving is the worst.

135
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:14,959
The way you eat...

136
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,319
