137
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:19,480
A breeding pig walks down a country lane.

138
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,879
I like it.

139
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,560
Hurry up, I've been hungry all day.

140
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,759
I left out the cilantro for you.

141
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,720
Thank you, Master.

142
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:36,000
Lei.

143
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:40,079
Remember last time we were on a case, there was a body...

144
