149
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:45,959
Pretty much the same.

150
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:46,839
Let me see.

151
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,279
Severely decomposed.

152
00:06:48,279 --> 00:06:50,800
These intestines, yeah, about the same.

153
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,360
Severely decomposed.

154
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,199
Come on, no, Lei.

155
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:53,959
Have one.

156
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,560
There will be plenty more of this in the future.

157
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:02,639
Eat.

158
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:03,439
Eat.

159
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,519
Come on, even Master said you should eat.

160
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,879
Just eat more, you...

161
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,680
I've thought of a way for you to die.

162
00:07:12,839 --> 00:07:13,600
Die from being annoying.

163
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,480
I'm happy to.

164
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,680
Alright, enough joking around.

165
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:17,680
Hurry up and tell me about the visits.

166
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,879
We've asked everyone we could nearby.

167
00:07:19,879 --> 00:07:20,759
No one knows anything.

168
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,360
The people who come to this nursery are regular customers.

169
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:25,079
No suspicious people have been seen.

170
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,040
Brother Lei,

171
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:30,040
Shouldn't you step out for a bit?

172
00:07:30,759 --> 00:07:31,959
No, I'm just listening.

173
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:34,519
I just served you your food.

174
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:36,279
And now you want me to leave? What do you mean?

175
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,439
Just step out for a bit.

176
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,800
Alright, Liu Ziming.

177
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,240
I'm leaving, okay?

178
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,480
I'm stepping out, alright?

179
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,680
I'm heading home, guys.

180
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,319
Bye, bye Brother Lei.

181
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:54,720
Master, what can't he know about?

182
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,160
We've all had a long day.

183
00:07:57,920 --> 00:07:59,399
Don't let him hang around here anymore.

184
00:07:59,439 --> 00:08:00,759
Let him go home and get some sleep.

185
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,680
You two,

186
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:05,720
one of you keep visiting people,

187
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:08,199
the other go to the police station to compare missing persons.

188
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:08,560
Yes.

189
00:08:08,560 --> 00:08:09,519
Then I'll go do the visits.

190
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:11,519
No, you come with me for the visits.

191
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:14,759
You go and carefully do the comparison.

192
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,240
Master, don't make me sit in the office.

193
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,040
I really can't sit still.

194
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,879
I'm begging you.

195
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:23,199
I'll go crazy, seriously.

196
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,199
If you weren't a cop,

197
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:27,920
you wouldn't have to sit for even a second.

198
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,160
Forget I said anything.

199
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:33,559
Hurry up and eat.

200
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:34,960
I'm eating, I'm eating.

201
00:08:47,519 --> 00:08:48,720
If you've already bought the house,

202
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,320
can you back out before taking possession?

203
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:52,960
It's probably not worth it, right?

204
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,320
They'll deduct a penalty for breach of contract and all that.

205
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:58,039
Master, are you in urgent need of money?

206
00:08:58,039 --> 00:08:58,919
I still have some.

207
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,679
It's nothing, I was just asking.

208
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:23,960
Don't blame me.

209
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:29,440
I really have no other choice.

210
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:35,559
If this well isn't filled in,

211
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,840
I won't be able to run my business at all.

212
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:41,039
Thank you.

213
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:49,320
Didn't he just leave?

214
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,960
Why did he come back?

215
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,960
Call the police, hurry, call the police!

216
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,879
Hurry, call the police! Call the police!

217
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,720
Call the police! Call the police! Call the police!

218
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:06,279
I... I just...

219
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,360
Take your time, don't rush.

220
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:10,360
I just feel uneasy inside.

221
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,960
I think it's a bad omen.

222
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,399
So today I came to burn some paper offerings for her.

223
00:10:14,399 --> 00:10:16,440
I thought I'd fill in the well while I'm at it, you see...

224
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:18,240
Take your time, don't rush, just speak slowly.

225
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:20,080
I mean, I... you... she...

226
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,720
She already... last time she...

227
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,600
I, I, I... Please calm down first.

228
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:25,639
Boss, I'll take him aside to calm down.

229
00:10:25,639 --> 00:10:26,720
And take a statement while we're at it.

230
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,080
Come on, this way.

231
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,440
No.

232
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,240
Last time, she... Come on, this way.

233
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:32,039
She already came here once before.

234
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:32,440
Right?

235
00:10:33,039 --> 00:10:33,519
After it was over...

236
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,240
Wait a moment.

237
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:44,360
Female, around thirty years old.

238
00:10:44,480 --> 00:10:45,399
Same as the previous one.

239
00:10:45,399 --> 00:10:46,559
A pair of underwear stuffed in her mouth.

240
00:10:46,679 --> 00:10:47,879
But she hasn't been dead for long.

241
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:49,000
No more than ten hours.

242
00:10:58,279 --> 00:10:58,960
Let's go.

243
00:11:02,399 --> 00:11:04,480
Zhang, hurry up!

244
00:11:04,639 --> 00:11:05,879
Copy that, Captain Liu.

245
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:07,399
Boss.

246
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:09,320
She also has a bit of cologne scent on her.

247
00:11:11,039 --> 00:11:12,799
Go check the boss's background.

248
00:11:13,159 --> 00:11:14,240
Could he be the one who did it?

249
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:16,039
Hard to say, just go quickly.

250
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,720
Yes.

251
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:18,159
Honestly, I really don't know.

252
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,120
Really?

253
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:21,639
Then where did you sleep last night?

254
00:12:22,279 --> 00:12:23,840
Your wife said you didn't come home last night.

255
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:26,399
I played cards outside all night yesterday.

256
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,159
My wife, you know...

257
00:12:28,159 --> 00:12:29,639
She wants to control everything.

258
00:12:30,159 --> 00:12:31,799
I didn't even dare tell her about this.

259
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:34,480
From October 2nd until today,

260
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,320
where have you been,

261
00:12:36,320 --> 00:12:37,000
who have you met,

262
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:37,720
what have you eaten,

263
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,200
write down clearly the times for each.

264
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:41,519
I...

265
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,600
It's been such a long time.

266
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:44,960
I'm afraid I can't remember it all clearly.

267
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:46,919
Don't you want to clear yourself of suspicion?

268
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,639
Do you want to clear yourself of suspicion or not?

269
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,600
Then think carefully.

270
00:12:51,960 --> 00:12:53,000
Think it through.

